  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You study magic at the Arcanamirium on Absalom Station, one of Dykon's or Pabaq's universities, or somewhere else. You might be a novice still learning the basics of magic while enjoying university life or an opinionated professor researching a niche subject.</p><p>Choose two attribute boosts. One must be to <strong>Intelligence</strong> or <strong>Wisdom</strong>, and one is a free attribute boost.</p><p>You're trained in your choice of the Arcana, Nature, Occultism, or Religion skill, based on your primary field of study, and the Academia Lore skill. You gain the Quick Identification skill feat.</p>"
